timelineItems.text: 83' - Garcia curls in a shot but Hall is there. #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Orlando City SC
timelineItems.text: '82 Garcia curcles a shot at goal from the edge of the box, it's an easy save for Hall who gets down to his left #TallyWall #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Matthew Kirby
timelineItems.text: Hally tips Saucedo's thundering effort on to the post. #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: CLOSE CALL! Orlando nearly doubles their lead but the header is rebounds off the crossbar. #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Jeremy Horton
timelineItems.text: 9' OCSC off the bar. #RSL lucky not to be down two.

timelineItems.name: Jordan
timelineItems.text: 5 minutes in and Kaká puts Orlando up 1-0! Fireworks at Rio Tinto tonight. #VamosOrlando #GoCity #GetWild

timelineItems.name: Lance Werner
timelineItems.text: Well, @OrlandoCitySC is playing with loads of heart now. Even down to 10, they are creating chances and holding the draw. #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Charles Barnard
timelineItems.text: A point isn't good enough tonight guys... #RSL

timelineItems.name: Sean Walker
timelineItems.text: 89' Mansally picks up a yellow card on a late challenge. Orlando holding off the siege. as Amobi Okugo checks in. #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: SC Ruckus
timelineItems.text: Tally Hall coming up huge right now. #GoCity #RSLvORL #TallyWall

timelineItems.name: VenessTravelMedia
timelineItems.text: And FIVE minutes of stoppage time?? From where??? #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Jason Ashcraft
timelineItems.text: Two games in which the other team is down a man and #RSL can't win? Prove me wrong

timelineItems.name: The Mane Land
timelineItems.text: 93' - Avila is fouled and Ramos applauds the call. lol, nice, Rafa. #RSLvORL

timelineItems.name: Patrick Clark
timelineItems.text: Maybe #RSL should have gone down a man. They play more dangerous when they're cornered. They look uninspired. #RSLvORL
